msg: Enable NetUIConfig JavaBean creation from the XMLBean.
Also switched this on for TypeUtils and for the IteratorFactory which now talk to the JavaBean for config information.
In order to make this work (without NPEs), this required wrapping a few other XMLBean elements in null checks while building said JavaBean config object.
